            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2401288-lynn-buschhoff?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer59298918" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8836863465911823774">For those of you who slept through modern American History and now feel ignorant, this is a great place to start feeling smart. The book spans those forgotten times between WWI and Watergate, and it is full or really interesting information. Manchester adds details about popular culture, that make history come alive. This is a book i might read again</span>

          </span>
        </div>


